              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Operators who want raw bulk AI articles for their own publishing pipeline.</div>
            <a href="https://byword.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tool-cta-btn">View pricing →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">03</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">Whalesync</div>
              <div class="tool-card-tag">Best Airtable to website sync</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">$59<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);">/mo</span></div>
              <div class="per">Starter plan</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it delivers</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>Two-way sync between Airtable / Notion and Webflow / WordPress</li>
                <li>No-code template pSEO at scale</li>
                <li>Real-time updates when source data changes</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>You still design templates and data tables yourself</li>
                <li>Per-row pricing scales with content volume</li>
