              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>Template quality determines ranking, not the tool</li>
                <li>Limited design flexibility vs full Webflow</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Founders launching their first programmatic SEO experiment.</div>
            <a href="https://pagefactory.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tool-cta-btn">View pricing →</a>
          </div>
